{"hcb10c8c3g9664g430cg89b5g721b95dabde0": ["I'm sorry, Arka.", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "a8e29214-7550-70b8-0099-354f99383708"], "hfc2c3ebegbb1ag4e50g9885g3a4f1f5e9f79": ["Don't be sorry - fetch some help!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "8d55b179-5a5f-0c16-20c0-e6a365f6cf2b"], "he026f97agce9dg4756g9344g3d0067fb0e22": ["Now? You wanna talk <i>now</i>?", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "28bf47cc-423f-9bda-36f2-6d6059f5899b"], "h807190a0g59fdg4ddag8965gb7969d10a403": ["Memnos? Where are you? He's not... he's not breathing!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "dfbb1373-ec6d-330c-c310-2618ace866cb"], "hae99de63g7abag4014g9103g01afc990e379": ["You idiot. Don't you do this to me!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "4653f642-7ff3-35c8-2200-f71ce652547b"], "h2ab0244dgf40eg406cgb35cg43c1058c3790": ["Someone help me! Kanon's dying!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "6f8e7b32-95f3-113c-ff57-0fdf880e384c"], "he78e7a87ga87eg4dd5g899cg1d3bba19f6cb": ["Kanon is dead. And so is Memnos.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "f0bb05f3-c2d2-9614-9f29-c2491b24074c"], "hb26c2b9fg670ag4695g8df3gb22b0456afe5": ["W-what?", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "9a0e8b4b-58ca-01d3-0680-0761ffb1aaac"], "h049f1906g3dc5g4293ga906g9a09a9f05405": ["Someone's going to pay for this.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "1222f99d-eb20-79b4-ae0d-7e24231831a7"], "h804a9415ge806g48c5g8c72g4f556b2e7fcd": ["Anyone in particular?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "b323aee2-309a-3eba-9526-878235e54657"], "h0a915d40g81a7g4f7cgbba5g98b8170a887b": ["A goblin we captured yesterday. I'm going to kill it.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "49c0c32a-6417-425b-6d61-8391bf7438ec"], "h3eab1991ga626g4872gbb25g310359e35a2b": ["<i>Stand aside.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "4b589094-cdfe-717d-24a7-ef7da648cc18"], "h4ccd3893g0288g4141gaf4ag13e1a71f4839": ["Your friends are dead - both of them. They need to be avenged.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "d3200951-c7fb-2cee-9801-7fed86395df7"], "hb03a6090gbe5ag4783ga3c4g587376eeb97a": ["Yes, they will.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "069b0dab-5f8b-227a-3e2e-a9c53b73cb27"], "h91276cf3g2153g4c9fgbcd4g7b75eb9936bd": ["<i>Place your hand on her shoulder.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "46a672a1-b7c1-408a-01a4-fcbd9f1c083d"], "h2040dce9g8835g48fagbc7eg1e533f00b251": ["No. I don't want your godsdamned comfort. I want <i>blood</i>.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "faf7570e-fea7-d419-51c4-b41e38ec8e3e"], "h9217efd7ge087g4904g973bg4c75f150a62e": ["The gods have taken him. All you can do is pray.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "237ad089-0059-e671-a47d-77f28e1a9c60"], "h4b1ddd45g3a66g4142g8fcdg74b042f2cb82": ["No. We've prayed enough. We've <i>lost </i>enough. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "9868e57a-bc13-a2be-6680-80cae5928079"], "h3fd8cd2ega0a6g414agbf3ag2de8f6993629": ["Memnos is gone too. Don't weep - they died well. Heroically. ", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "8fd4063e-4b7d-32a0-ff68-67e5058fcafe"], "hc685e886gfdd6g4010g99bcgf02698d5425d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "22f74f43-0cc2-55b8-c089-09a661d7c53d"], "h13bf5b6eg17e8g4abag9226gd19be503386b": ["Someone's going to pay for this.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "7d2c8c61-8d2a-d063-7020-c943be1153aa"], "h55e16014g11fag473ag814eg76f37813ebf2": ["Arka, no, wait! What are you doing?", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "825665ba-8bc7-0b12-3669-ae07361d25c3"], "h88e15990g8c4fg41c2gb359geae2589876c8": ["He's not breathing. Go find a healer!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "afcb6dcd-6387-4506-30a0-6df195c6b4ef"], "h8473c27cge647g4855g8f5ag56eb4c8c1b62": ["Do not embarrass yourself. He is gone.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "1485e33d-20d0-4450-2aa9-ddddcbda431f"], "he4e08fc0g9491g407agaa9eg811ddda7a201": ["It's too late. He's gone.", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "73692105-2d87-296e-6270-a41efdee53cd"], "h6c5fdd0bg2abcg4bb9g8de8gb71e81a7f483": ["No!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "ea686c2c-af74-98f9-067f-3cef886ff747"], "hd177a026g78dbg4976g8e7cg8b9676f2cf23": ["You need to avenge this - spill some goblin blood.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "af6c10a2-b90d-a270-e405-7f2d0d0a18d0"], "h56506c3dge3b7g4df3gbea2g60783da917dc": ["They'll slaughter us if we leave. There's nothing we can do.", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "f94b4846-209a-3364-2a7e-664e5a847900"], "hc509b1d8g00b6g4830g8494g7c88d331859a": ["They're slaughtering us now! ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "7c7abb2d-d412-38ee-b5b8-36dd34a1c456"], "hd55f743ag94a4g4c20gbd1eg2a273bcdaf1c": ["I'm sorry. It happened so fast.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "bc9433af-6df7-298e-e4d5-a8bd1c35af34"], "h003a29dbgd86eg461dgbcd7ge01f626bfb4c": ["He's dead. Stop wasting your time.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "fcc101fe-d582-ab7f-24b1-c4375bd2003a"], "h03b12fb3g5019g4c72gb517g75dbf1354f0f": ["You're... right. There's no point. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "812a3d9b-2a30-37ed-b3ee-3d39fd4b1da2"], "h96af76b6g9b37g473ega583gcb6b8bfb5fe2": ["I'll say a blessing to guide his soul.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "73b6d09c-c57f-9fc4-6a1b-57e39b7813c1"], "h8b415e89gf6ffg46a2g9a02g58831aef12b6": ["We'd like that.", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "b60760b0-0e68-2d52-1de4-a9c56d80b090"], "h75f6dd6dgb29cg4dc2gb2a8gfef4c4b371c0": ["No we wouldn't. It's pointless. ", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "913870e7-d883-ee04-f241-17af394a3ebb"], "hf15785c1gf3a5g4c71gb84cg90aa440c3dd3": ["No, no, no.", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "4f399fd3-ed63-77bb-3d6d-5857234265f2"], "ha97266dbg2c60g4ca4g9b24gbc592145bc74": ["It's... it's too late. Look at him.", "c3334ee5-38dc-4197-aacc-4aa55803ff52", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "602d5539-b20e-fa14-f0d7-e0b81e8046c7"], "hdfe6cce6g23deg40dcg8407ga5e1ff9deb4a": ["You idiot. Don't you do this to me!", "7ce0afc2-e8f2-4f2e-82d8-27df98acc3d8", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\DEN\\DEN_CapturedGoblin_GuardsGrieve.html", "068a4a1d-d21e-a6b4-4373-b80cac67e3e2"]}